    Examples

    Create a HTML widget using the ag-grid library

    aggrid.Rd

    This function creates a HTML widget to display matrix or a dataframe using ag-grid.

    Usage

    aggrid(
  data,
  columnDefs = NULL,
  defaultColDef = NULL,
  sortable = TRUE,
  filter = TRUE,
  resizable = TRUE,
  suppressRowClickSelection = FALSE,
  rowSelection = c("multiple", "single"),
  rowMultiSelectWithClick = FALSE,
  checkboxSelection = FALSE,
  pagination = FALSE,
  paginationPageSize = 10,
  domLayout = NULL,
  sideBar = FALSE,
  enableRangeSelection = TRUE,
  statusBar = TRUE,
  ...,
  theme = "ag-theme-balham",
  community = FALSE,
  use_cdn = FALSE,
  server = FALSE,
  width = NULL,
  height = NULL,
  elementId = NULL
)

    Arguments

    data

    dataframe

    columnDefs

    custom every column

    defaultColDef

    custom default column

    sortable

    Enable sorting? Defaults to TRUE.

    filter

    Enable column filtering? Defaults to TRUE.

    resizable

    Enable column resizable?

    suppressRowClickSelection

    Enable to suppress column select?

    checkboxSelection

    Enable checkbox in first column?

    pagination

    Enable pagination allows?

    paginationPageSize

    default size is 10.

    domLayout

    please see https://www.ag-grid.com/javascript-data-grid/grid-size/#dom-layout

    sideBar

    Include sidebar.

    enableRangeSelection

    Enable Cells range select?

    statusBar

    statusBar

    ...

    For more options, please see https://www.ag-grid.com/javascript-data-grid/grid-options

    theme

    Specify theme. Default is ag-theme-balham. please see https://www.ag-grid.com/example/?theme=ag-theme-alpine

    community

    Enable to use community?

    use_cdn

    Depends resource to use cdn?

    server

    server model

    width, height

    Width/Height in pixels (optional, defaults to automatic sizing)

    elementId

    An id for the widget (a random string by default).

    Examples

    aggrid(iris)

    

## use theme
aggrid(iris,theme = "ag-theme-alpine")

    

## auto size columns
aggrid(iris) |> auto_size_columns()
